item.title: Demensions - Over The Rainbow
item.description:
Somewhere
over the rainbow
Way up high

That I heard of
once in a lullaby

Skies are blue
and the dreams
That you dare to dream
really do come true
Someday I’ll wish upon
a star and wake up
Where the clouds
are far behind me
Where troubles melt
like lemon drops away

that’s where
